list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Remove .gitignore, add workspace.xml and update misc.xml
.gitignore file from the .idea directory was removed. This is due to the fact that it contains IDE-specific settings that shouldn't be tracked in the main repository.
A new workspace.xml file was added with various project settings.
The misc.xml file was updated, this change adds a first line indicating the xml version and its encoding. It's an essential part to ensure the correct parsing of an XML document.
